high_descs: Walk straight towards the dishwasher.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Turn right ahead a little, and then turn left to face the sink
Place the spoon in the cup that is in the sink.
Pick up the cup from the sink.
Turn left ahead a little, and then turn right to face the dishwasher.
Place the cup at the end of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a spoon in a cup.

high_descs: Walk to the dishwasher in front of you
Pick up the spoon on the counter above the dishwasher
Walk to the sink on your right
Put the spoon into the cup in the sink
Pick up the cup from the sink
Turn to the left and walk to the dishwasher on your right
Place the cup onto the counter above the dishwasher
anns.task_desc: Put the dirty dishes on the counter above the dishwasher

high_descs: Move to the counter  to the left of the sink and to the right of the microwave
Pick up the spoon from the counter
Move to the sink to the right of you
Place spoon into a cup in the sink
Pick up cup from the sink
Move to the counter to the left of the sink and to the right of the microwave
Place cup on to the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a spoon in it on the counter next to the microwave.
